messages.message: We've been experiencing a lot of flakiness with custom prompt validations - I've had this feature fail live a few times in a demo most recently with LuminAI. Can we please take a look at this? @Will McDermott would you be able to share your example project in the thread and the custom prompt validation that you used? cc: @lydia @Serena.
